svg:text.svg:tspan: A whole lot of royalty, not much loyalty... that
’s Macbeth in a nutshell. You’ll be pleased
to hear that this CGP book goes into much more detail — it explains the characters,
language, themes, historical background and more. Everything you need, in fact.
We’ve included bags of brilliant online extras too. There’s tailored activities for all the
big GCSE exam boards, and quizzes to test you on the whole play!
